Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:04.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:05.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Metro Police detectives\Nand the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love and mystery are\Nboth about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ain't that Hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?\NI can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just said on TV that Hide\Nwas going to be in the back-most car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, they did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But soccer victory parades are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every year, people get excited about Tokyo Spirits\Nbeing the front contender for the championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and this year, they finally managed\Nto win their first J1.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even the deciding match was\Na dramatic come-from-behind victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the clock was running down in\Nthe second half, they were losing 0 to 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Hide made it a tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after they went into overtime,\NNaoki scored the winning goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with all these people,\Nwe can't get a good view of the parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad, because I made sure\Nto bring my camcorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should've just\Nkept watching on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got the VCR going,\Nso we can all watch it afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! We might be able\Nto see it from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we get on top of that empty can bucket,\Nwe might get a better view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?\NCan you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gimme a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can see their heads,\Nbut not their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! If it were\Njust a bit higher, I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think there's anything\Nhigher than that empty can bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There he is, way over there!\NIt's Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Naoki's right\Nnext to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's facing\Nover here and waving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a second,\Nit's just getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know better than\Nto be climbing up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get them down\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a bit longer won't\Nhurt anything, old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't call me\Nan old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll put you under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Ndressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ditched work to come down here\Nand watch the parade, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:47.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha, that's why\Nyou're disguised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's not it!\NI've got my reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're here on a date,\Nisn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} in the boys' room\Nearlier, picking out a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going on a stealth date in disguise\Nwhile you're on duty, that's pretty slick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!\NThis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you ain't got\Nno place to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it all right for\Npolice officers to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's against regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's Japan coming to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I told you,\Nyou've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just work.\NThere's no date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Shiratori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you also\Nin disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got a weird fax\Nat HQ just a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It read,\N"I am Anti-Spirits."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Something interesting is going\Nto happen at the victory parade."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fax was a lot like one\NI'd dealt with in a previous case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we're here from\Nthe First Criminal Investigation Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the person in question\Nknows what we look like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so right now we're investigating\Nwhile in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it was just a lame prank\Nby a fan jealous of the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, so it wasn't a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The date in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be\Nnext week, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured there was no way you could wait\Nuntil next Sunday, so you got rash,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but maybe I was\Njust overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, h-how did you find out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, everyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were going to Tropical Marine Land\Nthat just opened, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\Nthe Japanese police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he books a holiday\Non your day off,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not hard to read\Nbetween the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear they all dragged Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} into\Nthe interrogation room to grill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he just up and confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like a whole bunch of guys\Nhave been gunning for that day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\Nthere's been a lot of reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to rent police binoculars\Nand radio equipment that day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me they're\Nplanning to stake us out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we go\Nto Tropical Marine Land too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Now see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just taking Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nto thank him for helping me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really, really telling\Nyou the truth. Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, are you going to give up\Nand watch, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... I'm not just going\Nto wave the white flag
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just because she\Nrejected my proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They still address each other\Nwith {\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and {\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have room\Nto make my way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm the one\Ntaking charge of this stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Date! Date! Today is a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's a date!\NThen the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yumi,\Ngive me a hand here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Look who's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-You dummy!\NShowing up at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw through that disguise\Nfrom a mile away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So my cover has\Nbeen blown, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't expect\Nto see you guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we surprised\Nall three of you officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, k-kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This disguise suits me well,\Ndoesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:43.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} Inspector Megure gave you orders\Nthat you didn't need a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why did you show up\Nlooking like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you understand, get out of that disguise\Nand go back to your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I wonder if I did something\NI shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. You just looked\Nlike {\i1}him{\i0} then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you were working at HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that detective had been placed at the First\NCriminal Investigation Division for only 7 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!\NThe car Hide is in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's push our way\Nto the front and get some video!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since I've been taping\Nall this time, there's not much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring\Nany extra tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So put it in\Nand get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if things\Nwill be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got that weird fax, right? The one that said\Nsomething would happen at this parade...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But all signs are suggesting\Nit was a prank after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what are you\Ndoing here, Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving out tickets\Nfor illegal parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of people leave their cars on\Nthe streets around here to watch the parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should probably hurry up\Nand move your own car, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or you'll be getting a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go do that right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys?\NWhere did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...\NSomebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a fan\Nof Big Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think\Nyou'd come to this parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to hex it,\Nso they wouldn't win next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:05.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did you go off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry and get some video,\Nthe car'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, key, key...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today must not be my day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone stole your camcorder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the midst of the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Unknown number"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My word...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancel the parade right now,\Nand evacuate the civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb.\NLooks like one car blew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Detective Takagi's car, was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then Detective Takagi got...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw someone earlier go up to the car\Nthrough an opening in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Shiratori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Where's Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It exploded right when he came up\Nto the car to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One does not ordinarily survive\Ngetting caught in such an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Detective Takagi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did say "ordinarily".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that\Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got away by the\Nskin of my teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so don't talk like\NI didn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to see\Na paper bag under the car
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that wasn't there when I parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just about to take it back to Inspector\NShiratori and ask if it might be a bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's a good thing you recognized that there\Nmight be a bomb inside the paper bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just told you about\Nthe fax we got at HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that was like one in a case\Nwe had dealt with before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If a detective were to have info\Nabout that serial bombing case,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and yet fail to notice that,\Nthen something is quite wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of failure to notice,\Nlook at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to have\Nnoticed that you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Takagi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}... Takagi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't, Sato!\NIt's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.95,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stay back!\NThis is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nyou're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm trying to lift up the car\Nand get him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s fine. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You burned the palm\Nof your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, we've got to get that\Nlooked at right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the one Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwas really trying to save was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Matsuda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb type is\Na plastic explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a time bomb,\Nbut a radio-detonator type.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, a cellular phone\Nor the like was used to set it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomber was probably watching\Nfrom somewhere near you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from where he could\Nhit the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that means that even though\Nthe bomb was of a different type,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just like the case\Nfrom three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is a good chance that the bomber\Nintends to kill police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:04.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep that in mind, and be careful\Nbut make a quick investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put everything you've got\Ninto catching the—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I might have gotten\Nthe bomber on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was taping\Nreally close to where the bomb was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then someone in the crowd\Nof parade watchers stole the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Stole?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But the tape's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't much tape left, so just before the\Ncamera got stolen, he switched the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video camera's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the tape was missing. It was thrown in\Nthe trash at the nearby subway station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means whoever stole the camcorder\Nwasn't interested in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but just the tape, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person who would do\Nsomething like that at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,would be a hardcore fan\Nof the Spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or someone who didn't\Nwant to be filmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like the bomber, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got it hooked up\Nto a big monitor for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mostly just Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I forgot and left the camera\Nrunning while it was pointing down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can hear you guys\Ntalking about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:38.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I {\i1}know{\i0} Inspector Megure gave you orders\Nthat you didn't need a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.\NThat's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you get\Njust that on tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just happened\Nto tape it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. It looks like\NSato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, well, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see someone behind Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nnext to his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems to be just a passer-by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And from this distance it's hard\Nto tell one person from another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, darn! The camera's\Npointing down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, the video ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like the footage\Nwe were hoping for,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the one who put the bomb in the paper bag\Nunder Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wasn't shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something was recorded\Nat the beginning, while I was in the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's rewind the tape\Nand take another look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!\NAnother bomb went off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one was at a phone booth\Nin front of the park in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately,\Nthere were no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Judging by the type of bomb,\Nit's probably the same person behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.\NContinue your investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. The way to get from the\Nsite of the first explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the park in Haido City...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's the Spirits'\Nvictory parade route!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the suspect is\Nnot targeting the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just someone who took his hatred\Nof the Tokyo Spirits way too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:31.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? How is\Nyour hand? I heard you burned it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no problem.\NI'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we've figured out\Nthe bomber's objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a good chance\Nhe's set up other bombs too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mobilize all officers in the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,get to the front of the route\Nand evacuate the nearby civilians,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,apprehend the suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put everything you got\Ninto finding the explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:21:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Ncontact the bomb squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have them standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nstay here and check the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you figure anything out,\Nget back to me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want to go\Nto the crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. You wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after this,\Nwe need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what is the bomber after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pretending to be the bomber\Nfrom three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}sending a fax to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and blowing up the car of\Na policeman who was dispatched...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:51.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then right after that, he blows up a phone booth\Nthat has nothing to do with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:56.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it really just about\Nhating the Spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Besides, this videotape\Nthat Mitsuhiko took...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:09.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is there something on it\Nthat will identify the bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:12.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:15.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what will it show?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you even watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've watched it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think someone in the crowd is suspicious,\Neveryone will look suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:24:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if you don't think anyone is suspicious,\Nnobody will look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the bomber {\i1}thought{\i0}\Nhe had been filmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though nothing\Nwas actually filmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:09.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nothing filmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:11.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:17.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.27,0:24:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Mail Van
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:23.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.10,0:24:24.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The case and the love come to a conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:25.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Isn't love prohibited?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:27.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Looks like a new year's almost here!
